race.description: Rq Supports Safety In Racing Mdn Hcp
race.comment: FILLYDELPHIA MISS (4) has been knocking on the door of a maiden victory placing in three of six overall and strikes a very winnable contest here. Rock-hard fit now and is sure to be right there at the business end. THE KOBAY TRAIN (6) has been thereabouts in recent efforts and gets in well at the weights with the 3kg claim from the low draw. Looks well placed to break the ice. ANNA CHATABOX (3) was in the market when facing the starter for the first time and where there's smoke there's fire. Top-three candidate with that debut effort now in the locker. LOUIS AUGUSTE (9) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough to feature in a contest of this nature. Can run a race while fresh. CHANTILLY QUEEN (5) is a last-start placegetter who should be underestimated.
